Use the function "ST_VLAD.m" to encode the features as presented in the paper:
"Spatio-temporal VLAD Encoding for Human Action Recognition in Videos".
Ionut C. Duta;  Bogdan Ionescu; Kiyoharu Aizawa; Nicu Sebe.
In International Conference on Multimedia Modeling, 2017.

In "demo.m" there is an example of using ST-VLAD encoding.
Please cite our work when using this code!


Ionut Cosmin Duta dutaionutcosmin@gmail.com
